            <scopecontent id="aspace_d47c832c185a0299cae000854f3412c9">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>The Transvaal Land Owners' Association materials are arranged in chronological order, and record the functions and activities of the association during the time in which E. H. Brocklehurst was a member. Documents in the series include business correspondence, rent statements, newspaper clippings, memoranda, membership renewal notices, quarterly reports, land revenue receipts and association meeting notices.</p>
            </scopecontent>
